WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.000
Welcome to RestoreAssist.

00:02.000 --> 00:06.295
In this tutorial, I'll show you how to sign in to your account.

00:06.295 --> 00:10.318
Step 1: Open your browser and navigate to restoreassist.au.

00:10.318 --> 00:12.636
The site loads in under 2 seconds.

00:12.636 --> 00:17.750
Step 2: Enter your email address and password, then tap the Sign In button.

00:17.750 --> 00:19.750
Step 3: You're now signed in.

00:19.750 --> 00:25.955
Your dashboard displays active jobs, upcoming inspections, and your workspace health score.

00:25.955 --> 00:30.000
That's it — you're ready to start managing restoration projects.